.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-6::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: fishing, singing
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: metal, trance
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, february
1. the fan of metal is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby         | fishing    | singing    |
| Music-Genre   | trance     | metal      |
| Birthday         | august | february |

