.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
There 2 different types of food: pepper, radish
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, dancer
There are 2 different nationalities: turkish, pakistani
1. the pakistani is on the left of the accountant##1
2. the turkish is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
3. the person eating pepper is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | radish | pepper     |
| Job     | dancer | accountant |
| Nationality   | pakistani | turkish    |

