.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-10::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, blend
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, singing
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
2. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | 7up     |
| Cigar       | blend        | havana    |
| Hobby      | filmmaking  | singing |

